{"tid":2514621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毅進男生心儀警嫂屢埋身被控遊蕩案，女事主反問辯方：「我丈夫係警察又點呀？」","createTime":"2021-05-03T11:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T11:51:17.000Z","uid":254745,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6b835938785919ab92094fbe2312f9499a82e657","tid":2514621,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:16:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>係你老母臭閪咩，好撚型咩，<br />\n<span class=\"green\">你老公</span>九成咪又係啲地底泥低賤<span class=\"blue\">藍衫</span><span class=\"blue\">散仔</span></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身材健碩的毅進學生疑為追求心儀美甲師兼「警嫂」，多番騷擾女方，包括到女方工作地點等放工再邀約出街，甚至涉尾隨女方上廁。女事主其後報警，涉案學生涉拒捕，遭武力制服。他否認遊蕩及意圖拒捕而襲警兩罪，今在九龍城裁判法院受審。辯方盤問女事主時，直指她丈夫的職業是警察，事主聞言反問：<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>「係又點呀？」</strong></span></span>她又投訴，被告今早在庭外質問她與丈夫：「咩料？夾埋屈我？」暫委裁判官黃子豪指被告違反保釋條件，並有妨礙司法公正之嫌，將會轉介警方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/3V5RSGT2DNAIFEZTSY53JAXHJQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2F3V5RSGT2DNAIFEZTSY53JAXHJQ%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=5038989f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2F3V5RSGT2DNAIFEZTSY53JAXHJQ%2F&h=fbd81263\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/3V5RSGT2DNAIFEZTSY53JAXHJQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HOk7SdH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHOk7SdH.jpg&h=4ce6bba3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89S6okn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89S6okn.jpg&h=fd5cf233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WOnmWGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWOnmWGE.jpg&h=57e0c